column5: Well as you are aware i am continuing the icefishing funniest photo contest again. Last year was funny indeed. Im hoping this year will be bigger and better. I would personally like to thank Rod Caster for his donation, it was gratiously received. I will do my part again as last year If anyone else would like to donate something that would be apreciated. I would like to have a 1rst, 2nd and third place winners this year. Its just for fun and give us a good chuckle juring winternet. I will post the rules and donations very soon. Thanks again And thank you kindly again Rod Caster, for you donation
